---
title: Steak with Silky Lemon Butter Broth plus Green Beans, Almonds & Rice
description: Lemon is our go-to ingredient for brightening up any meal, and this dish is bursting with citrusy goodness! You'll sear chicken cutlets, then add green beans, scallions, and butter to the pan, along with a squeeze of fresh lemon juice to create a flavorful broth. Serve alongside fluffy rice with almonds and lemon zest for a light, flavorful meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6729285f6db9cd4df46dfdaf-4d3c48b0.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/672bdc7015a18007ce687b43-en-US.pdf
